          - latency
          - success/failure status

[ ] 1.5 Build Workflow Rules
    - [ ] Full-file regeneration only
          - no partial edits
          - when a file changes, regenerate the entire file
    - [ ] No partial edits (explicit)
    - [ ] Commit after paste
          - paste → verify → commit
          - avoid “half-applied” changes
    - [ ] Metadata footer required
          - every file must end with a footer block
          - includes timestamps, dependencies, ML tags, version

